			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you need help setting up your own server farm in the cloud then I will happily assist you. I&#8217;m a total Cloud Convert, so helping other SMEs get into the cloud is something I&#8217;m evangelical about. I use <a href="http://scalr.net" target="_blank">Scalr</a>, which is SaaS AWS management tool, you will need to also sign up for this service before I can get started. There is a monthly cost of $99 to this. I am not affiliated with Scalr, or earn any referral revenues from them, I just think it&#8217;s a great tool that makes life a lot easier (and it costs next to nothing).</p>
<p>I charge $400 for this service and I do not develop your app, only build the farm on which it sits. I will talk you through the process and work with your developers to get you up and running. If I feel your app is particularly complicated that it may require extra time and costs, I will advise you up front of this. I will not charge more than the initial fee in most circumstances. Additional weekly consultancy is $100 a week, I am available on Google chat during UK office hours and most evenings. I don&#8217;t make any apologies for charging for set up. Once you know what you&#8217;re doing it is relatively uncomplicated, however, I am extremely busy running my own successful company <a title="Giant Digital" href="http://www.giant-digital.co.uk" target="_blank">Giant Digital</a> and I have been using this set up for over 2 years.</p>
<p>I accept PayPal. Get in contact using the contact form <a href="http://www.giant-digital.co.uk/contact.php" target="_blank">here</a> using the subject &#8220;business proposal&#8221;.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
